Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Course Overview", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.573719511312056*^9, 
  3.573719516762042*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"6c8cadd3-d208-4af2-9843-\
686538f686a0"],

Cell["\<\
The goal of this course is to show how to use the Wolfram \
Language\[Trademark] to carry out various operations in applied statistics. A \
basic working knowledge of the Wolfram Language and statistics will be \
assumed throughout the course. It should also be understood that a particular \
approach to statistics is not being advocated. That is up to the statistician \
and depends on the analysis being done. It is the intention of the course to \
give an illustration of what can be done using the Wolfram Language.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.573719533004735*^9, 3.573719801311317*^9}, {
  3.58003052676939*^9, 3.580030543216104*^9}, {3.580030626271303*^9, 
