d3f35e9edd26"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "In this example, you look at a typical example of easily read data, but a \
structure that is basically incompatible with doing any serious analysis. Use \
the ",
 StyleBox[ButtonBox["TemporalData",
  BaseStyle->"Link",
  ButtonData->"paclet:ref/TemporalData"],
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 " function to make the data useful for your analysis, while leaving it in a \
form that is easy for humans to read."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.5722647507722807`*^9, 3.572264840605751*^9}, {
   3.573721626944949*^9, 3.573721696155104*^9}, {3.573721833579204*^9, 
